Here's the copy-paste. This is for the main story and not the slice-of-life because I haven't read it yet.
Sometimes it just references random bands or IPs just for the sake of referencing them.
One example would be the IPod scene in chapter 16 where it just lists the bands they listened to. If replaced to something similar like "we listened to so many classic rock and metal songs", it could give the reader the freedom to insert what songs they could have played.
